sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Applicant as Applicant
    participant FE as React SPA
    participant API as ASP.NET Core API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant EmailQ as Email Queue<br/>(Channel)
    participant SMTP as SMTP / Mailjet
    actor Employer as Employer

    Note over Applicant,Employer: — Apply to Job —

    Applicant->>FE: Click "Apply" on JobDetails
    FE->>API: POST /api/applications/{jobId}<br/>Authorization: Bearer <jwt><br/>Body: { CoverLetter, ResumeUrl }

    API->>API: Validate user role = Applicant
    API->>DB: Check HasUserAppliedToJob(userId, jobId)
    alt Already applied
        API-->>Applicant: 409 Conflict — Already applied
    else User owns the job
        API-->>Applicant: 403 Forbidden — Cannot apply to own job
    else Job is inactive
        API-->>Applicant: 400 Bad Request — Job not active
    else Valid application
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO Applications<br/>(JobId, ApplicantId, CoverLetter, ResumeUrl)
        API->>DB: SELECT Job WHERE Id = jobId
        DB-->>API: Job (with EmployerId)
        API->>EmailQ: Enqueue ApplicationSubmitted email
        API-->>Applicant: 201 Created — Application object
    end

    Note over Applicant,Employer: — Background: Process Email Queue —

    EmailQ->>SMTP: Dequeue + Send email<br/>to Employer
    SMTP-->>Employer: "New application received for {JobTitle}"

    Note over Applicant,Employer: — Employer Reviews Application —

    Employer->>FE: View applications for job
    FE->>API: GET /api/jobs/{jobId}/applications
    API->>DB: SELECT applications with Applicant nav
    DB-->>API: List<Application>
    API-->>Employer: 200 OK — Applications list
    FE-->>Employer: Render application cards

    Employer->>FE: Update status to Interview
    FE->>API: PUT /api/applications/{id}/status<br/>Body: { Status: Interview }
    API->>DB: UPDATE Application SET Status = Interview
    API->>EmailQ: Enqueue ApplicationStatusChanged email
    API-->>Employer: 200 OK — Updated application
    EmailQ->>SMTP: Send status update to applicant
    SMTP-->>Applicant: "Your application status changed"
